.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
rmmod ice
modprobe ice
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.IP 2. 3
Enable hardware TC offload on the interface:
.INDENT 3.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
ethtool \-K <ethX> hw\-tc\-offload on
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.IP 3. 3
Disable LLDP on the interface, if it isn\(aqt already:
.INDENT 3.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
ethtool \-\-set\-priv\-flags <ethX> fw\-lldp\-agent off
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.IP 4. 3
Verify settings:
.INDENT 3.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
ethtool \-k <ethX> | grep \(dqhw\-tc\(dq
ethtool \-\-show\-priv\-flags <ethX>
.ft P
.fi
